{"tid":1974284,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"政府工/公務員vetting一問","createTime":"2020-04-15T17:33:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T15:59:44.000Z","uid":134802,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"337fd5acb45b9f224d7fae67763796ac742778bd","tid":1974284,"uid":134802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T17:33:45.000Z","msg":"代問 身邊有親戚細個唔記得衰啲咩 收過警司警戒 除左呢樣之外三代都清白<br />\n佢啱啱grad咗一年已經做緊嘢 唸住下年考eo<br />\n想問一下有冇巴打知收過警司警戒做唔做到高職公務員㗎？雖然eo又唔係真係話好高職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢唔知邊度聽返嚟話pt27以下嘅公務員vetting係唔會受警司警戒影響（因為呢個record理論上係過左18歲自動銷毀 唔會影響你良民證同埋移民嗰啲 但考eo vetting就唔知）我上網就唔係好搵到類似嘅case <br />\n佢又唔想浪費時間溫好耐書但vetting過唔到好似好笨柒咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />先唔好理佢過唔過到apt test JRE嗰啲先<br />\n想問有冇巴打有相關研究？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f3a6986900f80612613a99ee25d5ccfbb17e432","tid":1974284,"uid":86246,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T17:37:28.000Z","msg":"屌 親戚咁撚遠 仲要警司警戒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：唔識 不過我諗冇人確實答倒你"},{"pid":"a1d07f9e97f1cb03795dc55d8c58f9fd7a8c0d07","tid":1974284,"uid":134802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f3a6986900f80612613a99ee25d5ccfbb17e432","tid":1974284,"uid":86246,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T17:37:28.000Z","msg":"屌 親戚咁撚遠 仲要警司警戒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：唔識 不過我諗冇人確實答倒你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T17:39:44.000Z","msg":"sorry我講得唔夠清楚1999 我意思係親戚自己本人想考eo 個警司警戒係佢本人嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdc769061450235db96055250f8f475040135a46","tid":1974284,"uid":134802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T17:44:04.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets